{"tid":2315178,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【無品住客】台灣酒店床單滿佈大便+血跡不願賠錢　房務員無奈：整組都報廢了","createTime":"2020-12-07T04:51:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T10:48:15.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"5195aa51da7407db3a2eb0a8a7daccb64226e817","tid":2315178,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"受疫情影響，「Staycation」受港人歡迎，但有不少酒店業店都曾抱怨客人將房間弄至非常髒亂。台灣亦有一名酒店房務員遇到超無品住客，將酒店當作「戰場」，令床單滿佈血跡、屎跡，更不願全額賠償！<br />\n<br />\n掀開被單驚見暗藏血跡＋屎跡<br />\n台灣一名酒店房務員在Facebook群組「爆料公社」發文，表示前幾天整理房間時，不幸遇到超誇張的情況。她一進房時看到被子蓋著床，沒有多想就掀開，一打開卻見到床單滿佈大便跟血跡。由照片可見，被子充滿血跡，而床中心就有排泄物的痕跡，連帶枕頭也遭殃。<br />\n<br />\n她無奈表示，自己不清楚客人到底是因為剛好月經又想「開大」，抑或是因為肛交才會弄到這麼混亂。她相信沒有客人再敢睡在這套床單之上，因此只能報廢，並在社交網絡上向該名客人說明：<br />\n&quot;你如果有看到這篇文章，也請你不要只付2000元就了結，整組都報廢了，我們飯店都已經在虧損了，也請各位體諒一下我們房務人員，我們真的很辛苦了。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n網民好奇：整晚激戰都沒睡？<br />\n貼文引起不少網民留言，有不少網民覺得只收2000元（約500港元）太少，樓主表示整間房間已經消毒過，並換掉整組床單，總共花了一萬元，但跟對方要求賠償時，他們只願付2000元。<br />\n<br />\n大部分網民都直斥這對客人「自私」，認為這樣是蓄意破壞行為，應該報警處理。亦有人留言「那兩坨排泄物坐落的位置，難道是整晚激戰都沒睡嗎？」，好奇他們全晚到底睡在哪裡。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2821793/hotel_thumb_20201207_J_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2821793%2Fhotel_thumb_20201207_J_1024.jpg&h=1e807685&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2820000/2821793/phpPyGJHT_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2820000%2F2821793%2FphpPyGJHT_1024.jpg&h=80431493&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e31ca8060f827e3e96f73febd90e6f69d31724ac","tid":2315178,"uid":35420,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"做過咩先會搞到咁<br />\n好難想像<br />\n屌焄木眼屌到出血加賴屎？"},{"pid":"c09595a9e1c5448282186fe31784cfcd19a73245","tid":2315178,"uid":50660,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:53:58.000Z","msg":"點做到？想像唔到點玩先會咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064f77dd635471805ae95bcabdd7dfe748f46e0c","tid":2315178,"uid":3747,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:55:19.000Z","msg":"諗起Johnny Depp前妻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b138cab6f2a4bf964b935a2e387e08b90187adf1","tid":2315178,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"又要講句，呢D就高清大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94bcb75ce2ac870aaed3847dac2036a5f4a3f76b","tid":2315178,"uid":76063,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:56:54.000Z","msg":"肛交定sm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"194f1026b78d0f2065d9ddc37f7ca274f9a7d086","tid":2315178,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:58:27.000Z","msg":"m到 + 肛交 ....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3ac4b3be7b713829263ffe132bb55bead061515","tid":2315178,"uid":211941,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"菊花殘 滿地傷 你的床單已泛黃"},{"pid":"ad7b0a2eb498a8ac7b658b986fdabcb5ab4cc29c","tid":2315178,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b138cab6f2a4bf964b935a2e387e08b90187adf1","tid":2315178,"uid":54930,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T04:55:34.000Z","msg":"又要講句，呢